{"tid":1891723,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla 秘密開發 110kWh 大電池   續航距離超過 640 公里","createTime":"2020-02-22T04:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T14:56:39.000Z","uid":48083,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cd8f449974d62475c13ac3605d96ad0da7acc4d9","tid":1891723,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T04:58:54.000Z","msg":"今年一月有網民在網上爆料，指 Tesla 將會為旗下 Model S 和 Model X 改用全新電池，日前終於有證據顯示 Tesla 正在開發 110kWh 的新型電池，相信集團 CEO Elon Musk 早前透露的 640 公里續航距離目標，現在又再行近一步。<br />\n<br />\n第一個爆出 Tesla Model S P100D 車款的 Jason Hughes 是資深 Tesla 車主兼黑客，他最近在 Tesla 電池管理系統的程式碼中發現了全新「109kWh 可用電量」的電池資訊。將電池管理現有的緩衝區電量加入後，Hughes 相信 Tesla 的新型電池電量至少會達 110kWh，甚至高達 115kWh。<br />\n<br />\n除了 Model S 和 Model X 有望採用 110kWh 新電池，去年底有網民亦發現系統程式碼中出現了應用於 Model 3 的 100kWh 電池的描述，可惜至今 Tesla 都未有公佈和進一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n來源：teslarati<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/02/22/tesla-110-kwh-battery-pack-400-miles-range/life-tech/auto/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F02%2F22%2Ftesla-110-kwh-battery-pack-400-miles-range%2Flife-tech%2Fauto%2F&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=62ce06b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/02/22/tesla-110-kwh-battery-pack-400-miles-range/life-tech/auto/</a><br />\n<br />\n上海既廠房要100%國產，用唔用到新技術<br />\n係咪留咗一手防範支支反骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf61b0f38c955c5aef3afd210984c3165e9df8ae","tid":1891723,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:31:22.000Z","msg":"舊電係寧德時代定Panasonic 生產？"},{"pid":"f918f12313b25a94d8e36a0bed352d308fc28807","tid":1891723,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:49:35.000Z","msg":"FC鬥 FC鬥 FC鬥"},{"pid":"ea9a39a1994c764af56f7a3a4156cd786b5a8c0f","tid":1891723,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike"