:1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T07:49:07.000Z","msg":"唔係同嗰個咩寧合作咩"},{"pid":"1e119d0c71309bc6ae8e61c000893a31ffc78cf0","tid":1891723,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T07:49:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d42314249426a56b333407deee17b98a5fafc23c","tid":1891723,"uid":869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93db77e0dfb16a2e465cc7639006569c4cf0d065","tid":1891723,"uid":230416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:53:44.000Z","msg":"緩衝區電量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個concept係咪同240gb(256gb)/480gb(512gb)嘅ssd差唔多，啫係原本電池有一部份嘅capacity並冇劃分出嚟用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T07:52:59.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n專登留返一部分唔叉電, 因為完全叉滿舊電對壽命有影響"},{"pid":"89e83b014905a35b5a04cd33827a8f1c396e1b53","tid":1891723,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf61b0f38c955c5aef3afd210984c3165e9df8ae","tid":1891723,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:31:22.000Z","msg":"舊電係寧德時代定Panasonic 生產？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T07:53:09.000Z","msg":"週三 (19 日) 《金融時報》引述消息人士報導，電動車大廠特斯拉 (TSLA-US) 同意自寧德時代 (CATL) 採購磷酸鋰鐵 (LFP) 電池，以滿足其在中國工廠生產 Model 3 的電池需求。<br />\n<br />\n由於價格相較於含鎳、鈷電池低廉，LFP 電池被廣泛使用於中國電動車市場。英國 Benchmark Mineral Intelligence 分析師表示，特斯拉希望 LFP 電池的高能量密度特性能提高 Model 3 航程至 155 英里以上，以幫助該公司獲取中國電動車補貼。<br />\n<br />\n英國 Benchmark Mineral Intelligence 總經理 Simon Moores 稍早也於推特表示，特斯拉的陸製短程版 Model 3 將首度採用寧德時代的 LFP 電池。"},{"pid":"59593aba439f4366923940e219e7383c33ca5cb4","tid":1891723,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T07:59:10.000Z","msg":"星期一TSLA 上1000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4778766c14065abdbd1372cf45afaee5a7333ac5","tid":1891723,"uid":171668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"電動車+無人車+太空 = 未來<br />\n<br />\n蘋果都要收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAll in TSLA"},{"pid":"62d98e3ef9e91bafcc9c64a72fa022223c61aa6a","tid":1891723,"uid":63952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:53:34.000Z","msg":"股價GOGOGO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c84b33928dd2b1e31e6f5cc23ef717e6360b63","tid":1891723,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4778766c14065abdbd1372cf45afaee5a7333ac5","tid":1891723,"uid":171668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"電動車+無人車+太空 = 未來<br />\n<br />\n蘋果都要收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAll in TSLA"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:00:35.000Z","msg":"仲有太陽能板+hyperloop"},{"pid":"4dd41f3c4b1139cb77ddf48e767a4776d6f6ae03","tid":1891723,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T10:09:12.000Z","msg":"電池會佔全車重量六至八成??<br />\n電池會唔會大到車型變成七人車?<br />\n電池一次要叉幾個鐘?"},{"pid":"5163c9777f9f2aa4797a1bc8cf6948c52d46f44f","tid":1891723,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd8f449974d62475c13ac3605d96ad0da7acc4d9","tid":1891723,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T04:58:54.000Z","msg":"今年一月有網民在網上爆料，指 Tesla 將會為旗下 Model S 和 Model X 改用全新電池，日前終於有證據顯示 Tesla 正在開發 110kWh 的新型電池，相信集團 CEO Elon Musk 早前透露的 640 公里續航距離目標，現在又再行近一步。<br />\n<br />\n第一個爆出 Tesla Model S P100D 車款的 Jason Hughes 是資深 Tesla 車主兼黑客，他最近在 Tesla 電池管理系統的程式碼中發現了全新「109kWh 可用電量」的電池資訊。將電池管理現有的緩衝區電量加入後，Hughes 相信 Tesla 的新型電池電量至少會達 110kWh，甚至高達 115kWh。<br />\n<br />\n除了 Model S 和 Model X 有望採用 110kWh 新電池，去年底有網民亦發現系統程式碼中出